Subject: Web interface not working after upgrade from 11.5 to 12.0
Description: I have upgraded from 11.5 to 12.0 this morning and the web server appears to not be running. the services are running but getting a refused to connect. running a netstat -aob i cannot see a listener started for the port 8082
What_We_Know__c: Web Service is probably down/Local System mode
Next_Steps__c: Check in after the customer confirms
Solution_Comment__c: After changing we service run as to a proper user the problem was resolved.
Account_Name__c: Blackpool Teaching Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust
